ling by the chief guest Shri. K.P. Rajan, President Eriyad Grama Panchayath and Mr. Febin Francis, Thrissur District Coordinator Kerala State Biodiversity Board. Dr. K.H. Amitha Bachan then gave his speech and encouraged the volunteers from the Bhoomithrasea club of MES Asmabi College with his motivating words emphasising the requisite of niche specific ecological restoration of degraded ecosystems by the involvement of local community. A total of 32 students were volunteered in the mangrove planting in the 1, 22, 23 wards of Eriyad Grama Panchayath</p>','1','32',NULL,NULL,'Eriyad','1,22,23','16','49','programs','Recent','7,8',NULL,'2023-06-02 17:38:47',1,0,0,6,26,0,0,3,1,6,'3','8','127',NULL,1,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Marginalised',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Cell','1685956764.pdf',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'3',NULL,NULL),(199,160,'Webinar on Intellectual Property Rights and Artificial Intelligence','2023-05-25','2023-05-25','Online mode','Talk on IPR and AI','<p>IPR cell of MES Asmab College and IPR cell of St. Peter&#39;s College, Kolenchery together organized a webinar on IPR and AI. Dr. Basil Mathew, Assistant Professor of Political Science, St. Peter&#39;s College, Kolenchery delivered the talk. He talked about various aspects of IPR and discussed the role of IPR in AI. About 50 particpants were present in the webinar.</p>','7','43',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'0','0','Webinar','Cell','10',NULL,'2023-09-08 08:28:03',1,6,0,8,35,0,0,5,2,34,'187','8','160',NULL,1,27,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Cell','1694161937.pdf',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'8','Dr. Sayana K . A.',NULL),(200,154,'BLANGACHAAL SAMAGRA NEERTHADA PADHATHI','2021-09-07','2021-09-07','thevarplasa auditorium','Blangachalsamagratheerthada','<p>Sreenarayanapuram gramapanchayat &quot;Blangachalsamagratheerthada&quot; programme was inaugrated by Tyson Master (MLA Kaippamangalam ). Presidential address was by M.S Mohanan (president, SNpuram panchayat). Welcom